  <brief_title>Polymorphism of beta2-adrenoceptor and Regular Use of Formoterol in Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Polymorphism of beta2-adrenoceptor and Regular Use of Formoterol in Asthma: Preliminary Results</official_title>
